data.description: Welcome to the Estates of Roman Forest. This beautiful, nearly new 5 bedroom home features a ton of space for everyone.  2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms downstairs and 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and a large gameroom finish off the upstairs space.  This home sits on nearly 1/2 an acre with plenty of distance and space between your neighbors.  Enjoy entertaining your friends and family in this open concept living space featuring a beautifully appointed kitchen with white cabinetry, granite countertops and a large island.  The extended counters and storage space is perfect for serving food for your holiday gatherings.  The spacious primary suite overlooks the backyard and has a large ensuite featuring a soaker tub, separate shower and large walk-in closet.  Features include wrought iron spindles on stairway up to the nice sized gameroom.  3 car garage and widened driveway give you plenty of room for parking and storage.  No HOA.  Close to all amenities but far enough away to enjoy country living.
